  "title": "Sully's Peeves",
  "description": "I absolutely love the way Minecraft looks and feels, but I get easily bored and I thought it'd be fun to try and find the small things I would change about the textures!",
  "body": "<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\"><img style=\"float: right;\" src=\"https://i.imgur.com/uORDxrV.png\" width=\"617\" height=\"214\" /></span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\">I absolutely love the way Minecraft looks and feels, but I get easily bored and I thought it'd be fun to try and find the things I would change about the textures! A lot of these textures are very minimal and I don't expect you to see them all, but it's not meant to be very obvious anyway! I made this pack for fun and as a form of feedback to the artists at Mojang and I try to keep every change as loyal to the original as possible, some changes might change the whole texture others might only have one or two pixels changed! <br /><br />Ofcourse credits to the mojang artists for most of these textures, I only changed a little in most of these after all!</span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\">And credits to Tiptox for the amazing logo!!</span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 24px;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/amtXGlV.png\" width=\"1903\" height=\"1672\" /></p>\n<p>&nbsp;<img src=\"https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/767546664302804992/912728184116613140/horse.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"641\" height=\"971\" /><img src=\"https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/865186214427361300/960485996288417812/demo_background_-_kopie.png\" width=\"641\" height=\"355\" /></p>\n<p><img src=\"https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/667744248388517943/935486007493656576/Naamloos.png\" width=\"775\" height=\"531\" /><span style=\"font-size: 24px;\"><img src=\"https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/865186214427361300/934212253945831424/unknown.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"857\" height=\"490\" /><br /></span></p>\n<p>&nbsp;<img src=\"https://media.discordapp.net/attachments/865186214427361300/958333255214579774/unknown.png?width=1214&amp;height=683\" width=\"654\" height=\"736\" /><img src=\"https://static.planetminecraft.com/files/image/minecraft/texture-pack/2021/287/15116070-aa_l.webp\" width=\"654\" height=\"736\" /><img src=\"https://static.planetminecraft.com/files/image/minecraft/texture-pack/2021/287/14526425_l.webp\" width=\"654\" height=\"327\" /><img src=\"https://static.planetminecraft.com/files/image/minecraft/texture-pack/2021/287/15116041-aa_l.webp\" width=\"654\" height=\"433\" /><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/xpr7SNj.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"654\" height=\"433\" /></p>\n<p><img src=\"https://pbs.twimg.com/media/FHyHMt8WQAE_JFQ?format=jpg&amp;name=large\" width=\"654\" height=\"433\" /></p>\n<p><img src=\"https://pbs.twimg.com/media/FHyHLKkXIAIy4eR?format=jpg&amp;name=large\" width=\"654\" height=\"433\" /></p>",
